title: LUXURIOUS UNIT IN PARAMOUNT WORLD!!
posting_body: ['Enjoy this luxurious 3 bed, 4 baths plus Den, corner home in the sky.', 'Come up the semi-private elevator into your private foyer and enter this amazing 2,500sqft apartment with spectacular northeast views to the bay and city with custom built in walking closets, sheer curtains and blackouts, additional recessed lighting, subzero and wolf appliances.', 'Live at Paramount Miami Worldcenter and enjoy one of the buildings with most amenities in the world.', 'PMWC features virtual golf, 5 resort-style pools, yoga & recording studios, basketball court, spa, gym w/ boxing area, bbq kitchen, racquetball, kids area, soccer field, tennis courts, skydeck & observatory w/ telescopes.', 'Steps to Metro Mover, and more!', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
